Draft Release Checklist

1) Tag the release, eg:
   svn copy \
       https://gallery.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/gallery/gallery3/trunk \
       https://gallery.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/gallery/gallery3/tags/RELEASE_3_0_ALPHA_4

2) Build the release, eg:
   php build.php RELEASE_3_0_ALPHA_4

3) Publish the release to sf.net
   rsync -avP -e ssh dist/gallery-3.0-alpha-4.zip bharat@frs.sourceforge.net:uploads/

4) <insert docs about updating SF.net FRS stuff here>

5) Update sf.net, freshmeat.net stories

6) Publish gmc story


